spoon.support.visitor.clone

Class CloneBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • spoon.reflect.visitor.CtInheritanceScanner
      • spoon.support.visitor.clone.CloneBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CtVisitor

    public class CloneBuilder
extends CtInheritanceScanner
    Used to set all data in the cloned element. This class is generated automatically by the processor spoon.generating.CloneVisitorGenerator.
